Commentary Text: Jadeja to Rinku Singh, out Caught by Rayudu! Other than that last shot, he hasn't quite looked the part Rinku, perhaps because he's getting so low on a pitch where it's been stopping and sitting up - tennis-ball bounce if you will - and he gets too low to have a swat at this sweep to deep square leg.
